title: Coldplay - Live in the Amsterdam ArenA (2016)
description:
This torrent includes:
1. The full live concert of Coldplay in the Amsterdam ArenA from Thursday 23 June 2016 in mp3.
2. An mp4-video with a photo slideshow of the concert by 3FM (Dutch radiostation), for if you like to play it on your tv.
3. Setlist of the concert

~~~
Setlist
01. A Head Full Of Dreams
02. Yellow
03. Every Teardrop Is A Waterfall
04. The Scientist
05. Birds
06. Paradise
07. Always In My Head
08. Princess Of China
09. Clocks
10. Charlie Brown
11. Hymn For The Weekend
12. Fix You
13. Heroes (David Bowie cover)
14. Viva La Vida
15. Adventures Of A Lifetime
16. In My Place
17. Til Kingdom Come
18. I Walk The Line (Johnny Cash-cover)
19. Amazing Day
20. A Sky Full Of Stars
21. Up & Up

Note: Everglow was also included in the concert, but was not allowed to be on the recording.

Enjoy!
